[공지] 1theK YouTube는 MV를 유통하는 공식 채널로, 1theK에 업로드된 MV 조회수 또한 음악방송 순위에 반영됩니다.

BIBI, who made a strong impression by appearing on SBS' ‘The Fan,’ will make her official debut. 
BIBI's debut song ‘BINU’ is a song in the R&B/hip-hop genre. Since this song incorporates both rapping and singing simultaneously, it is expected to reveal BIBI’s differentiated style in full-scale. The song is known for its lyrics that leave an impression by having a unique perspective on soap.
